"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Directly building a metaverse may not be the best way. The user experience is terrible and it is difficult to popularize it to the public. However, it is an option to build a bubble universe in the original web2.0 world and open the portal to the metaverse. \\n\\nUsers can interact with metaverse through the interface in the web 2.0 world, and participate in the web3.0 experience without losing the 2.0 operating experience. \\n\\nGradually increase the number of portals, then merge the portals, and finally swallow the entire web 2.0 world, completing the transition to the metaverse.\",\"timestamp\":1641143403,\"title\":\"Capsule（8.6.2021）Metaverse Portal\"},\"digest\":\"ZmuvrX0TYAsDE5tQsjON3fLpkea1Ue4EjesFWI71ZJo\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xE828f8bE1a3CB994133936fB4D9A708a7D192462\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cWndKezD0ZiMgnYOqspWtyALlI_KYDziYOZaOerHeCY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kf7VHolS02uUcQvJnvpP7ci_9wxCwvj1KsxIdy1wyS4\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"qFn3Vue6sJR5fgX_ZcywnSm3or797d7QanHAL00ykPVzL43MWXuQa7PxKypQ5F4Kx--qnFG2rO63xIn93F46pg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x24845bd906a3dcd3a6a2c8def0e1867a94aa37e04d35018a13b94099ae5be24d4b1abdd27984d765963fd65aa852fe7e1dc6d3934335a6e14328e5bca1565db21b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"cWndKezD0ZiMgnYOqspWtyALlI_KYDziYOZaOerHeCY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Kf7VHolS02uUcQvJnvpP7ci_9wxCwvj1KsxIdy1wyS4\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"Ud_e35Kikzt9msuSbCinMSFidR6avP_F2RTHlzO4dyI\"}"